metadata.name: Milady x Ether Rocks #1
metadata.description: Milady meets Ether Rocks. Milady x Ether Rocks is an experimental collection of 1,200 pfpNFT inspired by the cutting edge art of Milady Maker and the on-chain provenance of Ether Rocks. This exclusive collaboration marks the debut of a visionary new art collective born from the hidden shadow council behind Milady Village and bunker1: Sprite 2. 'They made sprite 2 and its 2 guys' -Milady Angel Faye
